  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the equation above, <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> are constants. If the equation has infinitely many solutions, what are the values of <span class=\"italic\">a</span> and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> ?</p>\n",
